Available Tools: escalate_ticket | transfer_to_specialist | get_escalation_status | set_sla
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "ticket_id": "string", "reason": "string", "target_team": "string" }
Response Schema: { "ticket_id": "string", "escalated_to": "string", "reason": "string", "sla_hours": number, "status": "string" }
---
Question: The client is reporting unauthorized transactions on their credit card; escalate this urgently to the fraud department.
Call: { "func_call": "escalate_ticket", "ticket_id": "TKT-1029", "reason": "Unauthorized credit card transactions reported", "target_team": "fraud_team" }
Response: { "ticket_id": "TKT-1029", "escalated_to": "fraud_team", "reason": "Unauthorized credit card transactions reported", "sla_hours": 2, "status": "escalated" }

